com.registry

Class RegistryQuota

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.registry.RegistryQuota
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<RegistryQuota>

    public final class RegistryQuota
extends Object
implements Comparable<RegistryQuota>, Serializable

    A class which contains the size limits of the system registry. The class holds information for the maximum size and the current size of the system registry.

    Since:
